data.title: William David Grose
data.text:
Dave, 72, of Phoenix passed away Wednesday November 15, 2017 after a long battle with several medical issues. Dave was born in Charleston, West Virginia and moved with his family to Phoenix as a one-year-old. Dave spent the rest of his life in Arizona. He was a graduate of Orangewood Elementary, Sunnyslope High School, Glendale Community College and Arizona State University. He enjoyed time working with dogs as a trainer, breeder and Dog Show participant. Karaoke singing and photography were great passions. Preceded in death by his father and mother. Survived by his two children Michael Grose; Mishelle (Grose) Haupt (husband Dirk Haupt and daughters Ashlee and Emilee Haupt) of Phoenix; and brothers Jim from Glendale and Don from Tucson. Services are private. Visit https://hansenmortuary.wpengine.com for condolences.
